<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Karl von Tüngen zu Reußenburg</head><p>Der Rat gewährt Mose Bok, Jude des Adressaten, und seiner Ehefrau bis Martinstag Geleit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_331" id="164v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_331_r2l24">Karln von Tüngen ʒum <expan>Reẅſſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_331_r2l25"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Karl . als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von Moſſe Boken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l26">eẅrs Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der nehſt von vns vrlawb <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l27"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wıe wol vns ſölıch ſache niht wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l28">füklıch ſeyn . doch vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvellen wır <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Moſſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l29">Juden . <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> weıb vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab . für awſʒlewt . geleyt bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l30">geben <expan>hıeʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> ſand Merteins tag <expan>ſcherıſtkom<ex>m</ex>end</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l31">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_331_r2l32"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_331" id="164v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Karln von Tüngen zum <expan>Rewssemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Karl, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von Mosse Boken ewrs juden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der nehst von uns urlawb
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und wie wol uns sölich sache niht wol füklich seyn, doch umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> wellen wir <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        Mosse juden, <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> weib und
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab für awszlewt geleyt bey uns geben
                                <expan>hiezwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Merteins tag
                                        <expan>scheristkom<ex>m</ex>end</expan></q>11.11.1421</note>
</app> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
